ementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"e4a2ba3\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Special Session Paper Submission Instructions \u2013 ICAIC 2025<\/h3>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1ce5651 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"1ce5651\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<style>\/*! elementor - v3.21.0 - 18-04-2024 *\/\n.elementor-widget-text-editor.elementor-drop-cap-view-stacked .elementor-drop-cap{background-color:#69727d;color:#fff}.elementor-widget-text-editor.elementor-drop-cap-view-framed .elementor-drop-cap{color:#69727d;border:3px solid;background-color:transparent}.elementor-widget-text-editor:not(.elementor-drop-cap-view-default) .elementor-drop-cap{margin-top:8px}.elementor-widget-text-editor:not(.elementor-drop-cap-view-default) .elementor-drop-cap-letter{width:1em;height:1em}.elementor-widget-text-editor .elementor-drop-cap{float:left;text-align:center;line-height:1;font-size:50px}.elementor-widget-text-editor .elementor-drop-cap-letter{display:inline-block}<\/style>\t\t\t\t<p data-start=\"176\" data-end=\"323\">Authors are invited to submit their research papers to the <strong data-start=\"235\" data-end=\"255\">Special Sessions<\/strong> of ICAIC 2025. Please follow the guidelines below for submission:<\/p>\n<h5 data-start=\"325\" data-end=\"371\"><strong data-start=\"329\" data-end=\"369\">Step 1: Access the Submission Portal<\/strong><\/h5>\n<p data-start=\"372\" data-end=\"503\">Visit the <strong data-start=\"382\" data-end=\"399\">Microsoft CMT<\/strong> submission system: <a href=\"https:\/\/cmt3.research.microsoft.com\/ICAIC2025\" target=\"_new\" rel=\"noopener\" data-start=\"424\" data-end=\"501\">ICAIC 2025 Submission Portal<\/a><\/p>\n<h5><strong data-start=\"509\" data-end=\"553\">Step 2: Select the Special Session Track<\/strong><\/h5>\n<ol data-start=\"556\" data-end=\"752\">\n<li data-start=\"556\" data-end=\"638\"><strong data-start=\"559\" data-end=\"569\">Log in<\/strong> to your Microsoft CMT account or create one if you are a new user.<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"639\" data-end=\"683\">Click on <strong data-start=\"651\" data-end=\"681\">&#8220;Create a New Submission.&#8221;<\/strong><\/li>\n<li data-start=\"684\" data-end=\"752\">Choose the appropriate <strong data-start=\"710\" data-end=\"735\">Special Session Track<\/strong> from the list.<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<h5><strong data-start=\"758\" data-end=\"820\">Step 3: Paper Formatting Guidelines (Springer LNNS Format)<\/strong><\/h5>\n<ul data-start=\"823\" data-end=\"1226\">\n<li data-start=\"823\" data-end=\"911\">Papers must follow the <strong data-start=\"848\" data-end=\"908\">Springer Lecture Notes in Networks and Systems format<\/strong>.<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"912\" data-end=\"989\"><strong data-start=\"914\" data-end=\"933\">Maximum Length:<\/strong>&nbsp;10-15 pages (including references, figures, and tables).<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"990\" data-end=\"1014\"><strong data-start=\"992\" data-end=\"1008\">File Format:<\/strong> PDF<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"1015\" data-end=\"1152\"><strong data-start=\"1017\" data-end=\"1039\">Template Download:<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/www.springer.com\/gp\/computer-science\/lncs\/conference-proceedings-guidelines\" target=\"_new\" rel=\"noopener\" data-start=\"1040\" data-end=\"1150\">Springer LNNS Templates<\/a><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h5><strong data-start=\"1232\" data-end=\"1261\">Step 4: Upload and Submit<\/strong><\/h5>\n<ol data-start=\"1264\" data-end=\"1474\">\n<li data-start=\"1264\" data-end=\"1339\"><strong data-start=\"1267\" data-end=\"1295\">Enter submission details<\/strong>, including title, abstract, and keywords.<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"1340\" data-end=\"1388\"><strong data-start=\"1343\" data-end=\"1378\">Upload the formatted manuscript<\/strong> in PDF.<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"1389\" data-end=\"1427\">Review all information carefully.<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"1428\" data-end=\"1474\">Click <strong data-start=\"1437\" data-end=\"1447\">Submit<\/strong> to complete the process.<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<h5><strong data-start=\"1480\" data-end=\"1521\">Step 5: Confirmation &amp; Review Process<\/strong><\/h5>\n<ul data-start=\"1524\" data-end=\"1727\">\n<li data-start=\"1524\" data-end=\"1593\">A <strong data-start=\"1528\" data-end=\"1550\">confirmation email<\/strong> will be sent upon successful submission.<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"1594\" data-end=\"1647\">Acceptance notifications will be sent according to the conference schedule.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p data-start=\"1729\" data-end=\"1779\">\ud83d\udccc <strong data-start=\"1732\" data-end=\"1777\">Submit early to avoid last-minute issues!<\/strong><\/p>\n<p data-start=\"1781\" data-end=\"1876\">For queries, contact the <strong data-start=\"1806\" data-end=\"1832\">Special Session Chairs<\/strong> or visit the official ICAIC 2025 website.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Special Sessions Special Session 1 Advancements in Computational Intelligence for Real-World Problem Solving Special Session 2 AI-Driven Cybersecurity: Advancements, Challenges, and Future Directions Special Session 3 Future Fusions of Innovation: Generative AL, Cloud Security, Blockchain and sustainability for a Smarter World Special Session 4 Artificial Intelligence and its Application Special Session 5 Contribution of Computer [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"_monsterinsights_skip_tracking":false,"_monsterinsights_sitenote_active":false,"_monsterinsights_sitenote_note":"","_monsterinsights_siten